Class IAddon

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.holoeverywhere.addon.IAddon
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AddonTabber

    public abstract class IAddon
extends java.lang.Object
    Basic class-holder of addons
    This class implement a storage for all type-specified addons, like IAddonActivity and IAddonFragment
